rComments: Prof Joshua is so good ! He is willing to help you out of class and gives you good feedback . He teaches super clearly but one thing miserable is weekly quizzes, forcing you to study. Recommend him, I have learned a lot from his class !

Had International Organizations. Libben is a solid prof, extremely approachable about literally any questions relating to your essay, final, midterm, etc. Clear, uses contemporary examples, and really tries to make sure you understand the relevance of everything he says. Would take again without thinking twice. No textbook (but lots of readings).
